{
  "stem": "9665.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, we have got a lot of people coming here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they need to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "See, when you got to that convent and you were 10 kilometers inside Switzerland, they didn't-- the Swiss police didn't do anything to you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Once they caught you within 10 kilometers, then you were lost, because it is an international law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you come from one country, you have to send them back to that country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So France libre, that so-called unoccupied France, when you came, they should deliver you back to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They delivered you to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Swiss-- and I would like to make that statement-- were very, very pro-German during wartime, because they allowed the trains from Germany to go right through their territory-- if they were neutral, they shouldn't allow that-- to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is my opinion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Joseph Schmidt went over the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a famous man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put him on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got TB.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what TB is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he died within four weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a famous singer, Joseph Schmidt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If I got that name wrong, then I will correct that later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went back to Lyon, all time changing the sauf-conduit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got some new ones in between.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But naturally, if you were holding it up with this color, you could see there is a little bit of-- how would you call it-- forgery in there, right?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I bought some new ones from another policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to Jacquet and I told him about the monastery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a lot of officers coming from Holland, a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say a few hundred every month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was eight or nine months in France.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
